Class LevelThree

java.lang.Object
java.util.Observable
com.example.demo.levels.LevelParent
com.example.demo.levels.LevelThree
public class LevelThree extends LevelParent
LevelThree defines the game logic for the third level, including enemy spawns and progression to the next level.
